你是個拒絕服兵役者
You're a conscientious objector,

606
00:37:23,220 --> 00:37:25,740
- 那你還來參軍 - 你誤會了 長官
- and you joined the army? - Well no, sir.

607
00:37:26,810 --> 00:37:29,180
我只是堅持反對暴力而已
I'm... I'm a conscientious cooperator.

608
00:37:30,630 --> 00:37:32,170
你是在耍我嗎 道斯
Are you screwing with me, Doss?

609
00:37:32,190 --> 00:37:34,130
我沒有 長官 我是自願參軍
No. No, sir. I volunteered.

610
00:37:34,700 --> 00:37:37,480
不管是穿軍服 敬禮
I got no... no problem with wearing my uniform,

611
00:37:37,500 --> 00:37:39,720
還是盡我的職責 我都沒問題
or saluting the flag and... and doing my duty.

612
00:37:39,740 --> 00:37:44,050
只是 持槍殺人 是絕對不行的
It's just... just carrying a gun and taking a human life.

613
00:37:45,000 --> 00:37:47,360
你不殺生 是這個意思嗎
You don't kill. That's all?

614
00:37:47,380 --> 00:37:48,550
是的 長官 是這個意思
Yes, sir. That's all.

615
00:37:48,570 --> 00:37:51,150
你知道戰場上 幹的就是殺人勾當嗎
You know quite a bit of killing does occur in a war.

616
00:37:51,700 --> 00:37:52,240
我知道 長官
Yes, Sir.

617
00:37:52,260 --> 00:37:54,650
殺戮就是戰爭的本質
I mean that is the essential nature of war.

618
00:37:54,730 --> 00:37:55,550
是的 長官
Yes, sir.

619
00:37:55,940 --> 00:37:56,940
好吧
Alright.

620
00:37:58,010 --> 00:38:00,980
那你對美國陸軍還有什麼其他要求嗎
Do you have any other requirements of the United States army?

621
00:38:01,380 --> 00:38:03,040
為了能讓您在這裏 和我們一起生活得舒心
Is there anything else that we can do to ensure

622
00:38:03,070 --> 00:38:04,860
還有什麼我們能為您做的嗎
that you have a comfortable stay here with us?

623
00:38:04,880 --> 00:38:07,560
他不想在週六執勤 長官
He doesn't wanna work on Saturday, sir.

624
00:38:07,590 --> 00:38:10,970
週六是... 我信奉安息日會
Well, Saturday is... I'm a Seventh Day Adventist.

625
00:38:11,000 --> 00:38:14,420
週六是安息日 所以
So... saturday is my sabbath, so...

626
00:38:14,450 --> 00:38:16,170
我不能工作
I'm not allowed to work then.

627
00:38:16,200 --> 00:38:17,620
在我看來 這完全不成問題
I don't think that poses a problem,

628
00:38:17,640 --> 00:38:18,660
你覺得呢 中士
do you, Sergeant?

629
00:38:18,830 --> 00:38:21,370
考慮到道斯二等兵是個虔誠的信徒
We should simply ask the enemy not to invade on the Sabbath,

630
00:38:21,390 --> 00:38:23,240
我們應該通知敵人 讓他們別在週六發動進攻
'cause Private Doss here is a prayer.

631
00:38:24,320 --> 00:38:26,990
好了 事情已經很清楚了
Alright. Now we got that clear.

632
00:38:28,220 --> 00:38:30,310
現在 我來跟你說說我的要求吧
Now let me tell you my requirements.

633
00:38:30,430 --> 00:38:32,490
不像你的要求那麼複雜
They're not as complicated as yours.

634
00:38:32,520 --> 00:38:33,750
我的要求很簡單
They are very simple.

635
00:38:34,760 --> 00:38:37,720
只要你還在這個軍營 只要你還是我的兵
As long as you're in this company under my command,

636
00:38:37,890 --> 00:38:39,940
你就得遵守我的命令 完畢
you will obey my orders. Period.

637
00:38:41,800 --> 00:38:43,030
如果在這裏 你都不能服從命令
If you can't do it here,

638
00:38:43,050 --> 00:38:45,650
那麼在戰場上 我就更不能信任你
I can't trust you to do it in the battle.

639
00:38:50,260 --> 00:38:50,980
我會用第八條例來處理你
I'm putting you in

640
00:38:51,010 --> 00:38:53,940
以精神問題為理由 遣送你回去
for a Section 8, psychiatric discharge.

641
00:38:55,050 --> 00:38:56,050
解散
Dismissed.

642
00:38:57,060 --> 00:38:57,910
各位
Gentlemen!

643
00:38:59,040 --> 00:39:01,160
我想向你們介紹一下 戴斯蒙德·道斯二等兵
I want you to meet Private Desmond Doss.

644
00:39:01,890 --> 00:39:02,890
顯而易見
Apparently,

645
00:39:03,370 --> 00:39:05,760
道斯二等兵反對暴力
Private Doss does not believe in violence.

646
00:39:06,210 --> 00:39:07,800
他絕不會採取暴力行動
He does not practice violence.

647
00:39:08,080 --> 00:39:10,190
甚至不會屈尊去碰武器
He will not even deign to touch a weapon.

648
00:39:11,300 --> 00:39:12,700
道斯二等兵
You see, Private Doss

649
00:39:13,380 --> 00:39:15,490
是一位拒絕服兵役者
is a conscientious objector.

650
00:39:16,020 --> 00:39:17,520
在此 我請求各位
So I plead with you,

651
00:39:17,920 --> 00:39:20,710
在戰場上 就別指望他來救你們了
do not look to him to save you on the battlefield,

652
00:39:21,770 --> 00:39:23,790
因為他肯定會
because he will undoubtedly

653
