be too busy wrestling with his conscience to assist.

654
00:39:27,550 --> 00:39:29,190
中士 不是這樣的 中士
Sarge, that's not true, Sarge.

655
00:39:29,210 --> 00:39:30,500
二等兵 別說話
Private, as you were.

656
00:39:34,210 --> 00:39:34,990
我知道
Now, I realize

