For Pete's sake, Smitty give him back his Bible.

673
00:40:25,620 --> 00:40:27,490
我可沒跟你說話
I don't remember speaking to you.

674
00:40:31,540 --> 00:40:32,990
你為什麼不動手呢
So, how come you don't fight?

675
00:40:33,640 --> 00:40:35,440
你是不屑跟我們動手嗎
You think you better than us?

676
00:40:36,130 --> 00:40:37,130
不是
No.

677
00:40:37,850 --> 00:40:39,300
