Nice.

699
00:41:31,310 --> 00:41:32,320
傳過來看看
Hey, pass it around.

700
00:41:32,820 --> 00:41:34,760
只有真正的英雄才配得上
Now, this would be the kind of broad

701
00:41:35,580 --> 00:41:37,180
