that deserves a real man.

702
00:41:38,540 --> 00:41:39,740
把照片還給我
Give me that back.

703
00:41:40,940 --> 00:41:41,680
求我
Please.

704
00:41:43,760 --> 00:41:44,430
求你
Please.

705
00:41:45,400 --> 00:41:47,090
"求你 史密提 把照片還給我"
"Please give it back, Smitty."

706
00:41:48,110 --> 00:41:50,110
求你 史密提 把照片還給我
Please give it back, Smitty.

707
00:42:00,410 --> 00:42:02,430
你有出現幻聽嗎 戴斯蒙德
Do you hear voices, Desmond?

708
00:42:05,610 --> 00:42:06,610
沒有 長官
No, sir.

709
00:42:07,380 --> 00:42:09,750
根據我的理解 上帝會跟你說話
But I understand that God talks to you.

710
00:42:09,780 --> 00:42:10,810
對嗎
Is that right?

711
00:42:11,020 --> 00:42:12,770
長官 我並不是個瘋子
Sir, I'm not a crazy person.

712
00:42:12,940 --> 00:42:15,640
那大家都認為你瘋了
Then how you feel... most people regard you,

713
00:42:15,670 --> 00:42:17,520
你有什麼感受呢
