衝啊
Go!

1263
01:22:01,350 --> 01:22:03,110
- 上啊 - 來吧
- Let's go! - Come on!

1264
01:22:39,990 --> 01:22:41,160
醫護兵
Medic!

1265
01:22:43,960 --> 01:22:47,430
我來了 用手壓住這裏 用手壓住
I'm here. Put your hand on it. Put your hand on it!

1266
01:23:18,290 --> 01:23:19,360
上 上 快上
Go, go, go!

1267
01:23:34,390 --> 01:23:36,560
鬼二 鬼二
Ghoul. Ghoul.

1268
01:23:38,450 --> 01:23:40,510
你沒事吧 你那裏受傷了
You're okay? Where you hit?

1269
01:23:43,890 --> 01:23:45,860
你頭被撞了下 沒事的
You got a bump on the head, that's okay.

1270
01:23:46,930 --> 01:23:48,140
你叫什麼名字
What's your name?

1271
01:23:49,000 --> 01:23:50,440
- 安迪 - 全名呢
- Andy. - Andy what?

1272
01:23:51,260 --> 01:23:52,260
安迪·沃克
Andy Walker.

1273
01:23:52,830 --> 01:23:54,050
外號是什麼
Also known as?

1274
01:23:55,620 --> 01:23:56,920
- 鬼二 - 鬼二
- Ghoul. - Ghoul.

1275
01:23:56,940 --> 01:23:59,020
鬼二 你沒事的 你沒事的
Ghoul, you're okay. You're okay.

1276
01:24:03,890 --> 01:24:04,980
幹得不錯 兄弟們
Good job, men.

1277
01:24:05,140 --> 01:24:06,140
幹得漂亮
Good work.

1278
01:24:06,630 --> 01:24:07,410
今晚好好休息
Dig in for the night.

1279
01:24:07,430 --> 01:24:08,530
只要我們守住這裏
We hold this spot.

1280
01:24:08,560 --> 01:24:10,690
明天就能掃平整個山嶺
We mop up the rest of the ridge tomorrow.

1281
01:24:11,930 --> 01:24:13,010
現在 孩子們
Okay boys.

1282
01:24:13,500 --> 01:24:15,330
都給自己找個舒服的安全窩
Find yourself a nice safe hole.

1283
01:24:15,340 --> 01:24:16,610
躲在掩體裏 或者待邊上也行
In or near the bunker.

1284
01:24:16,640 --> 01:24:18,380
每兩小時換崗放哨
Rotate watch every two hours.

1285
01:24:18,640 --> 01:24:19,980
我們都不知道外邊還有什麼
We don't know what's out there.

1286
01:24:20,010 --> 01:24:21,630
所以 盡量放低身體
Heads down, asses lower.

1287
01:24:21,810 --> 01:24:23,520
任何不說英語的人 都格殺勿論
Shoot anything that don't speak English.

1288
01:24:23,550 --> 01:24:24,580
包括格雷斯嗎 中士
That includes Grease, Sarge?

1289
01:24:24,650 --> 01:24:25,790
尤其是他
Particularly him.

1290
01:24:26,450 --> 01:24:28,650
我不管你是要撒泡尿 還是蹲大號
I don't care if you need to take a piss or a dump.

1291
01:24:28,860 --> 01:24:30,630
都不能獨自出去
It ain't safe to go out there alone.

1292
01:24:32,560 --> 01:24:34,250
道斯 你他媽要去哪裏
Where the hell you going, Doss?

1293
01:24:35,450 --> 01:24:37,200
報告中士 外邊還有很多傷員
Still more wounded out there, sarge.

1294
01:24:37,980 --> 01:24:38,860
我跟他一起去
I'll go with him.

1295
01:24:39,510 --> 01:24:41,440
機靈點 小心行事
Be smart, keep your ears down.

1296
01:24:43,440 --> 01:24:45,430
好了 大家先找地方吧
All right, let's find a spot.

1297
01:24:52,430 --> 01:24:55,360
開戰不到十五分鐘 瓦拉利和亨利就死了
Rinnelli and Henry dead in the first 15 minutes.

1298
01:24:55,400 --> 01:24:56,980
直接掛了
Just straight off.

1299
01:24:58,190 --> 01:24:59,400
真是乾脆
It's straight off.

1300
01:25:00,610 --> 01:25:01,610
彼德森
Peterson.

1301
01:25:01,640 --> 01:25:02,640
大眼
Popeye.

1302
01:25:03,690 --> 01:25:05,030
斯坦福和墨菲
Stanford and Murphy.

1303
01:25:05,730 --> 01:25:07,220
佩奇和昂格爾
Page and Unger.

1304
01:25:09,380 --> 01:25:10,750
還有拉斯頓.
Ralston

1305
01:25:11,620 --> 01:25:14,350
"和平年代 黑髮人送白髮人"
"In peace sons bury their fathers."

1306
01:25:15,420 --> 01:25:18,280
"戰爭到來 白髮人送黑髮人"
"In war fathers bury their sons."

1307
01:25:20,480 --> 01:25:22,740
別說這些喪氣話了 行嗎
You wanna stop spouting that crap?

1308
01:25:24,510 --> 01:25:25,860
沒有任何作用
It don't help none.

1309
01:25:27,230 --> 01:25:28,230
是啊
Yeah.

1310
01:25:29,040 --> 01:25:30,490
你說的沒錯
Yeah, you got that right.

1311
01:25:30,960 --> 01:25:31,960
在這是沒用
Not here.

1312
01:25:36,260 --> 01:25:37,260
讓我來吧
Give me that.

1313
01:25:44,200 --> 01:25:44,900
喂
Hey!

1314
01:25:45,030 --> 01:25:45,380
喂
Hey!

1315
01:25:45,410 --> 01:25:47,080
這位腹部受傷
We got an abdominal wound.

1316
01:25:47,800 --> 01:25:49,320
這兄弟需要輸點血
This lad is gonna need some plasma.

1317
01:25:49,340 --> 01:25:50,480
- 沒問題 - 交給我們吧
- You got it. - Leave him with us.

1318
01:25:50,510 --> 01:25:51,910
好的 你安全了
Okay. You're okay now.

1319
01:25:52,170 --> 01:25:53,410
他們會照顧好你的
They got you.

1320
01:26:02,040 --> 01:26:03,630
我們要不要找個地方 吃點東西
Should we find a hole and dig in?

1321
01:26:04,610 --> 01:26:05,810
是個好主意
Sounds good to me.

1322
01:26:07,070 --> 01:26:08,210
把鋼盔戴上吧
Put your helmet on.

1323
01:26:18,340 --> 01:26:19,600
你不來點嗎
You ain't gonna eat that?

1324
01:26:22,450 --> 01:26:23,580
我不吃肉
I don't eat meat.

1325
01:26:23,800 --> 01:26:24,800
你吃吧
Help yourself.

1326
01:26:26,490 --> 01:26:27,820
你當然不吃肉了
Of course you don't.

1327
01:26:37,050 --> 01:26:38,780
她可真是漂亮
That's one heck of a dame.

1328
01:26:41,180 --> 01:26:41,990
你真是配不上這個美人
You know you're fighting out of

1329
01:26:42,020 --> 01:26:43,470
你知道這點 對嗎
your weight class with her,don't you?

1330
01:26:50,980 --> 01:26:51,980
是的 我知道
Yes, I do.

1331
01:26:54,330 --> 01:26:55,430
可別這麼跟她說
Don't tell her that.

1332
01:26:56,220 --> 01:26:58,170
她要是和我這樣的人在一起 肯定會更幸福
She'd be much happier with a man like me anyway.

1333
01:26:58,200 --> 01:26:59,900
沒錯 不過等她認清你就不會了
Yeah, until she got to know you.

1334
01:27:01,760 --> 01:27:03,420
有時候 我確實挺混蛋的
I'm an asshole sometimes.

1335
01:27:04,160 --> 01:27:05,160
只是有時候嗎
Sometimes?

1336
01:27:08,980 --> 01:27:10,340
你說的沒錯 好吧
You're alright. Alright.

1337
01:27:36,960 --> 01:27:38,430
這些日本人很狡猾
These Japs are sneaky.

1338
01:27:40,060 --> 01:27:41,480
我來放第一班哨
I'll take first watch.

1339
01:27:41,620 --> 01:27:43,100
你先休息會吧
And you get some shut-eye.

1340
01:28:28,710 --> 01:28:29,780
肯定是場噩夢
Hell of a dream.

1341
01:28:48,020 --> 01:28:49,880
我夢到 敵人用刺刀殺死了我
Dreamed I got myself skewered.

1342
01:28:50,870 --> 01:28:52,220
而我卻毫無辦法
I couldn't do nothing.

1343
01:28:53,760 --> 01:28:54,960
槍就在這裏
Rifle's just there.

1344
01:29:00,080 --> 01:29:01,080
不會咬人的
It won't bite.

1345
01:29:02,710 --> 01:29:03,710
不對 它會的
Yeah, it will.

1346
01:29:06,290 --> 01:29:07,170
看看周圍死的人
Look around you.

1347
01:29:07,550 --> 01:29:09,020
在經歷這一切之後
After what we've just been through,

1348
01:29:10,050 --> 01:29:12,010
任何正常人 就會拚命想要武器
any sane man would be screaming for a weapon.

1349
01:29:12,030 --> 01:29:13,840
我可沒說過 我是正常人
I never claimed to be sane.

1350
01:29:20,060 --> 01:29:21,590
我爸爸是個酒鬼
My daddy is a drunk.

1351
01:29:24,130 --> 01:29:25,350
多年以來 他一直想戒掉
He fought it for years,

1352
01:29:25,370 --> 01:29:27,060
但始終沒能成功
but it kinda got a hold of him hard.

1353
01:29:27,090 --> 01:29:28,340
所以脾氣很糟糕
Made him mean.

1354
01:29:28,770 --> 01:29:29,440
至少你還知道自己父親是誰
Least you knew him.

1355
01:29:29,460 --> 01:29:30,840
而我父親卻可能是十來個男人中的任意一個
Mine could've been any one of the ten guys

1356
01:29:30,870 --> 01:29:32,650
而且他們誰都不配 所以...
and none of them would worth a damn, so...

1357
01:29:34,840 --> 01:29:36,350
所以 是你媽媽把你養大的嗎
So, your momma raised you?

1358
01:29:36,410 --> 01:29:37,200
我記得她
I knew her.

1359
01:29:37,280 --> 01:29:39,620
但在我五歲時 她就把我送進了孤兒院
But she gave me to an orphanage when I was five.

1360
01:29:39,640 --> 01:29:40,980
從此就再沒見過她
Never saw her again.

1361
01:29:43,270 --> 01:29:44,840
我學會了麻利做事
I learned how to act quick.

1362
01:29:46,550 --> 01:29:47,720
學會了迅速識人
Learned how to judge people quicker,

1363
01:29:47,750 --> 01:29:49,450
但卻看錯你了 大錯特錯
and I got you very wrong.

1364
01:29:59,290 --> 01:30:01,160
我爸經常揍我和我哥
My daddy used to beat me and my brother

1365
01:30:01,190 --> 01:30:03,990
太陽上山的時候打 太陽下山的時候抽
just because the sun rose and then whip us because it set.

1366
01:30:06,920 --> 01:30:08,120
這點我都能忍
I could take that...

1367
01:30:10,710 --> 01:30:12,950
但當他對我媽動手的時候
but when he would do it to our momma...

1368
01:30:12,970 --> 01:30:14,910
你給我滾開 死女人
Get away from me, woman!

1369
01:30:22,640 --> 01:30:24,390
夠了 再也不許這樣
That's enough. No more.

1370
01:30:24,960 --> 01:30:25,920
聽見了嗎
Do you hear me?

1371
01:30:25,950 --> 01:30:27,710
你他媽的開槍啊
Pull that damn trigger.

1372
01:30:27,900 --> 01:30:30,750
不要 戴斯蒙德 住手
Don't, Desmond. Stop!

1373
01:30:37,460 --> 01:30:38,550
但你並沒有殺了他嗎
But you didn't kill him?

1374
01:30:41,380 --> 01:30:42,950
在我心裏 已經殺了
In my heart, I did.

1375
01:31:04,870 --> 01:31:06,600
所以 在那之後 我向上帝發誓
So that's why I made my promise to God,

1376
01:31:06,630 --> 01:31:09,210
我絕對不會再碰槍了
I ain't never gonna touch a gun again.

1377
01:31:13,780 --> 01:31:15,900
我還是不跟你講我的事了 因為你就是個瘋子
Well, I ain't giving you mine, 'cause you're crazy.

1378
01:31:39,110 --> 01:31:40,370
狗娘...
Son of a...

1379
01:31:43,030 --> 01:31:44,290
王八蛋
Son of a bitch！

1380
01:32:13,110 --> 01:32:14,410
撤 撤 快撤
Go! Go! Go!

1381
01:32:20,160 --> 01:32:23,340
快撤 快撤 都快撤回來
Move! Move! Get your asses over here!

1382
01:32:23,370 --> 01:32:25,800
我們也... 我們撤 快撤 撤
Why don't we... let's go. Go! Go!

1383
01:32:43,220 --> 01:32:46,460
撤退 回撤 快撤
Fall back, fall back! Go!

1384
01:33:01,040 --> 01:33:02,740
他們從地道裏出來的
They're coming from underground!

1385
01:33:04,090 --> 01:33:06,710
探照燈 這裏是B6 請求立即支援
Searchlight, this is Baker Six. Request immediate support.

1386
01:33:06,740 --> 01:33:08,860
目標位置 YT5-1-5
Target is at Yoke-Tare-Five-One-Five.

1387
01:33:08,880 --> 01:33:10,010
難道你不知道...
Don't you notice...

1388
01:33:10,050 --> 01:33:11,890
當然 我當然知道我們正在這鬼地方
Yes! Yes, I notice that's where the hell we are,

1389
01:33:11,910 --> 01:33:14,290
但我們很快就要守不住了
but I don't expect to be here much longer!

1390
01:33:15,160 --> 01:33:16,770
我請求了炮火支援
I called an artillery strike!

1391
01:33:16,800 --> 01:33:19,620
撤退 快撤 快撤
Fall back! Move! Move!

1392
01:33:25,720 --> 01:33:27,890
撤退 全體 撤退
Fall back! Men, fall back!

1393
01:33:33,360 --> 01:33:34,360
這有敵人
Get some!

1394
01:33:55,810 --> 01:33:58,230
兄弟 我在這裏 就在這裏
Hey, buddy. I'm right here, right here.

1395
01:34:05,950 --> 01:34:06,680
好吧
Okay.

1396
01:34:07,570 --> 01:34:08,370
掩護我
Cover me!

1397
01:34:11,970 --> 01:34:12,970
快撤 快撤
Go! Go!

1398
01:34:25,400 --> 01:34:26,740
別過來 孩子
Get out of here, kid!

1399
01:34:30,130 --> 01:34:31,650
來這裏 孩子
Come here, son!

1400
01:34:34,960 --> 01:34:36,290
你知道該怎麼辦
You know what to do.

1401
01:34:36,570 --> 01:34:37,900
用力按住
Keep pressure on it.

1402
01:34:41,400 --> 01:34:43,080
不用 我不需要血漿
No! Don't need plasma.

1403
01:34:43,110 --> 01:34:44,080
給他用吧
Give it to him!

1404
01:34:44,110 --> 01:34:45,110
在那邊
Over there!

1405
01:34:45,550 --> 01:34:46,750
我沒事的 去吧
I'll be okay. Go.

1406
01:34:46,900 --> 01:34:47,720
快去
Go!

1407
01:34:48,210 --> 01:34:48,910
- 胖球 - 怎麼了
- Greasy! -What?!!!

1408
01:34:48,940 --> 01:34:51,000
- 把爾文送回去 – 好的 沒問題
- Get Irv back! - You got it, okay.

1409
01:34:51,020 --> 01:34:52,730
那好 咱們回見
Okay, see you soon.

1410
01:34:57,910 --> 01:34:59,780
來吧 快來
C'mon. C'mon!

1411
01:35:03,310 --> 01:35:05,810
我們得馬上撤離 來吧 加油
We gotta move right now! C'mon! C'mon!

1412
01:35:27,830 --> 01:35:29,670
撤退 撤退
Fall back! Fall back!

1413
01:35:30,570 --> 01:35:32,100
撤 撤 快撤
Go, go, go!

1414
01:35:35,120 --> 01:35:36,540
小心手雷
Fire in the hole.

1415
01:35:39,380 --> 01:35:40,320
換這個
Change.

1416
01:35:46,200 --> 01:35:47,980
你得盡快離開這裏
You'd better get the hell out of here!

1417
01:35:48,000 --> 01:35:49,670
快撤 快撤
Move! Move!

1418
01:36:33,630 --> 01:36:35,330
我好怕 我好怕啊
I'm scared. I'm scared.

1419
01:36:35,640 --> 01:36:36,970
這個能止疼
It's going to help the pain.

1420
01:36:39,740 --> 01:36:41,610
別 別 不要 你不能這樣
No! Don't! Dont'! Don't you do that!

1421
01:36:41,630 --> 01:36:42,550
堅持住
C'mon!

1422
01:36:43,120 --> 01:36:44,570
堅持住 史密提 堅持住
C'mon, Smitty, you stay with me!

1423
01:36:44,590 --> 01:36:46,130
我們走 我們得撤離
Let's go. We gotta move!

1424
01:37:07,460 --> 01:37:09,090
幫我把他送下去
Hey! Help me get him down.

1425
01:37:09,120 --> 01:37:10,520
幫我把他送下去
Help me get him down!

1426
01:37:11,640 --> 01:37:12,930
快點 抬他下去 快點
Come on. Let's move. Come on.

1427
01:37:12,950 --> 01:37:15,060
沒法幫你了 兄弟 他不行了
Can't help you buddy. He's gone.

1428
01:37:15,270 --> 01:37:17,700
- 不會的 - 快點 我們得趕緊離開這裏
- No. - Come on! We gotta get out of here!

1429
01:37:17,720 --> 01:37:18,720
快走
Let's go!

1430
01:37:20,640 --> 01:37:21,810
快點 走吧
Come on, let's go.

1431
01:37:31,050 --> 01:37:32,610
快點 所有人
Come on! Everyone!

1432
01:37:33,200 --> 01:37:34,200
快下懸崖
Off the ridge!

1433
01:38:12,490 --> 01:38:13,960
主啊 你要我怎麼做呢
What is it You want of me?

1434
01:38:22,590 --> 01:38:23,860
我不能領會
I don't understand.

1435
01:38:30,410 --> 01:38:32,130
我沒法傾聽
I can't hear You.

1436
01:38:33,470 --> 01:38:35,550
救護兵 救救我
Medic! Help me!

1437
01:38:35,820 --> 01:38:37,070
救救我
Help me!

1438
01:38:38,750 --> 01:38:39,920
主啊 救救我吧
Help me, Lord!

1439
01:38:44,730 --> 01:38:45,730
好吧
Alright!

1440
01:39:04,120 --> 01:39:06,780
- 有人會好好照顧你的 - 輕點 輕點
- You're in good hands. - Easy does it. Easy.

1441
01:39:07,710 --> 01:39:09,150
六... 八
Six... Eight...

1442
01:39:10,770 --> 01:39:11,560
十四
14.

1443
01:39:12,200 --> 01:39:14,510
- 馬上把他們送到安全的地方 – 遵命 長官
- Get these men secured immediately. - Yes, sir.

1444
01:39:14,840 --> 01:39:16,100
二等兵福特 下來了幾個人
Private Ford. How many?

1445
01:39:17,380 --> 01:39:18,950
只有三十二人下來 長官
32 only came down, sir.

1446
01:39:19,790 --> 01:39:20,990
- 老天爺 - 走吧
